# ── Cross-cutting alignments to ai: governance dimensions ────────────────────
# Maps ITIL practices and principles to canonical ai: dimensions for SPARQL
# queries that cross both the SKMS and domain layers.

skms-skos:KnowledgeManagement          skos:relatedMatch ai:Transparency .
skms-skos:InformationSecurityManagement skos:exactMatch  ai:Security .
skms-skos:RiskManagement               skos:exactMatch  ai:Accountability .
skms-skos:ServiceContinuityManagement  skos:relatedMatch ai:Robustness .
skms-skos:AvailabilityManagement       skos:relatedMatch ai:Reliability .
skms-skos:WorkforceAndTalentManagement skos:relatedMatch ai:HumanOversight .
skms-skos:MeasurementAndReporting      skos:relatedMatch ai:Transparency .
skms-skos:ServiceLevelManagement       skos:relatedMatch ai:Reliability .
skms-skos:SupplierManagement           skos:relatedMatch ai:Accountability .
skms-skos:FocusOnValue                 skos:relatedMatch ai:Sustainability .
skms-skos:OptimiseAndAutomate          skos:relatedMatch ai:Sustainability .
